											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="&quot;These are the toys that were donated by the toymaker! We should be careful with them.&quot;&#xD;&#xA;We didn't know they had explosives in them. We only read the note about them having something inside, which sounded dangerous. But now we look at them and see - indeed, something is wrong with them. We can't use Arfur's name, only the toymaker (not merchant!)" />
